The,Battery,Status,API,documented,by,W,C,is,a,browser,based,API,that,enables,web,developers,to,discover,the,battery,life,of,a,hosting,device,This,enables,web,application,features,to,be,dynamically,catered,to,a,device,s,battery,status,improving,power,efficiency,and,user,experience,The,API,dependences,include,EcmaScript,and,WebIDL,version,The,Battery,Status,API,was,historically,packaged,within,the,W,C,System,Information,API,but,was,excluded,to,promote,additional,efficiency,and,easier,implementation,Documentation,for,the,API,is,in,the,form,of,a,brief,written,by,W,C,and,representatives,from,Intel,and,Google,including,code,samples,and,additional,reference,material